Subject: Secunia Research: Autonomy KeyView wosr.dll Data
	Block Parsing Buffer Overflow

====================================================================== 
 
                     Secunia Research 28/07/2010
 
  - Autonomy KeyView wosr.dll Data Block Parsing Buffer Overflow -
 
====================================================================== 
